- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is likely because the paper presents a new sampling method for picking ballots randomly from a stack. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is likely because the paper discusses the distribution of chosen ballots and the design of mitigation procedures. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is possible because the paper presents a new method for sampling ballots that does not require identification numbers or counting many ballots per draw.
